                "name": "Hypnotic Hood",
                "ability_type": "Supernatural",
                "ability_type_abbrev": "Su",
                "text": "A psyche serpent can use the hypnotism occult skill unlock (<i>Pathfinder RPG Occult Adventures</i> 195) to implant suggestions as a full-round action (instead of taking 1 minute) an unlimited number of times per day. While it hypnotizes its targets, it sways from side to side with the spiral pattern of its hood fully displayed. A successfully hypnotized victim can recall this spiral pattern but otherwise has no memory of the act of hypnotism unless the psyche serpent wishes it to."
            },
